If you're feeling stressed, it's understandable you'd want to relax and put your feet up. Unless of course you're driving a vehicle on the highway. An undated video, which has surfaced on social media, shows a taxi driver driving on the M1 highway, near the Glenhove off-ramp in Johannesburg, with what appears to be his leg dangling out of the window. How he managed to drive like that - let alone that he did - had social media users flummoxed: